\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8423559\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8423559\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104utv1665703530936.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/utv1665703530936.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/utv1665703530936.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"utv1665703530936\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify diagnostic settings for the current Debugger session.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"utv1665703530936__p_d175751e1_d175752e1_d175753e1\">For information on the settings available on each tab, choose the tab, then press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">F1</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"utv1665703530936__p_d175754e1_d175755e1_d175756e1\">The settings that you apply become the active settings for the current debugging session.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"utv1665703530936__section_rrd_frh_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567887e63\">Settings Buttons</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Understand the buttons that might display for the Debugger settings.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"utv1665703530936__ul_n4q_grh_tcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"utv1665703530936__li_d53573e1_d53574e1_d53575e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Apply</span>—apply the\n               settings.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"utv1665703530936__li_d53576e1_d53577e1_d53578e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span>—apply the settings\n               and close the form.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"utv1665703530936__section_kfx_hrh_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567887e85\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Go to <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Preferences</span></span> and ensure that <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">On close: save state &amp;\n               preferences</span> is selected.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"utv1665703530936__p_d175769e1_d175770e1_d175771e1\">To save the settings under a specific name, click\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"utv1665703530936__p_d175772e1_d175773e1_d175774e1\">Enter a name and description and choose\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Apply</span>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ibc1665703531301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: I/O Print</a><p>Choose the level of I/O messages that are displayed in the message frame or transcript window.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yno1665703531917.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Triggers</a><p>Choose the triggers you want to be enabled or disabled for debugging, or those that you want to be set as breakpoints.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ppp1665703531653.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Tracing</a><p>Choose the level or type of ProcScript-related tracing to be displayed in the message frame or transcript window.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uha1665703532184.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Errors</a><p>Set a specific ProcScript error value ($procerror) as a breakpoint.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sev1665703532366.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Message Frame</a><p>Specify whether the clrmess ProcScript instruction is enabled or disabled, and whether application messages are sent to the application's message frame or to the application's transcript window.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423559\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423559\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Debugger Settings Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify diagnostic settings for the current Debugger session. For information on the settings available on each tab, choose the tab, then press F1 . The settings that you apply become the active settings for the current debugging session. Settings Buttons Understand the buttons that might display for the Debugger settings. Apply —apply the settings. Close —apply the settings and close the form. How to Go to View > Preferences and ensure that On close: save state & preferences is selected. To save the settings under a specific name, click Add . Enter a name and description and choose Apply . Related Links Settings: I/O Print Choose the level of I/O messages that are displayed in the message frame or transcript window. Settings: Triggers Choose the triggers you want to be enabled or disabled for debugging, or those that you want to be set as breakpoints. Settings: Tracing Choose the level or type of ProcScript-related tracing to be displayed in the message frame or transcript window. Settings: Errors Set a specific ProcScript error value ($procerror) as a breakpoint. Settings: Message Frame Specify whether the clrmess ProcScript instruction is enabled or disabled, and whether application messages are sent to the application's message frame or to the application's transcript window. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}